research_municipality_step.notes: Fate, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government, which aligns with the mayor_council type. Andrew Greenberg is the current Mayor. The City Council members are elected by 'Place'. While a recall petition against Codi Chinn was filed in January 2026, she remains a Council Member as of the current date, with a recall election pending in May 2026.
